{"title":"乞丐难当","authors":["池北偶"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"乞丐难当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶　诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人的地狱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富人的天堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由世界里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乞丐也难当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张口不管事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸手不灵光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能靠弹琴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能凭卖唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想要讨面包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得出新花样："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或装扮塑像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或粉墨登场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施用苦肉计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"求路人解囊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少种造型，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行乞在路旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为此新景观，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这般怪现状。（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐玉明摄于西班牙巴塞罗那市中心伦巴拉大街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝海青摄于德国科隆大教堂前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尤　胜摄于加拿大街头"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}